Jean Marchat https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Marchat 0 Jean Marchat (1902–1966) was a French film actor who appeared in around fifty films during his career. He made his film debut in 1931 and appeared in Maurice Tourneur's Departure the same year. Jean_Marchat ( 1902 – 1966 ) was a_French_film_actor who appeared in around_fifty_films during his_career .
